{
  "name": "getTextBroadcast",
  "description": "Returns a single TextBroadcast instance for a given text broadcast id",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "id": {
        "format": "int64",
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "An id of a text broadcast"
      },
      "fields": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Limit fields received in response. E.g. fields: id, name or fields items (id, name), see more at [partial response](https://developers.callfire.com/docs.html#partial-response) page."
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "id"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "https://api.callfire.com/v2/texts/broadcasts/{id}{?fields}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "A text campaign allows you to send a text message to a number of recipients. It supports scheduling, retry logic and pattern-based messages",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**bigMessageStrategy**: If message length exceeds 160 characters, multiple messages will be sent, SEND_MULTIPLE strategy is chosen by default. Available values: SEND_MULTIPLE - send text as multiple messages, DO_NOT_SEND - do not send text if it exceeds 160 characters, TRIM - trims text message to 160 characters",
            "**fromNumber**: A phone number in E.164 format (11-digit) or short code. Example: 12132000384, 67076, etc",
            "**id**: A unique id of a broadcast",
            "**labels**: A labels of a broadcast",
            "**lastModified**: A time when the given resource was updated, formatted in unix time milliseconds (read only). Example: 1473781817000",
            [
              "**localTimeRestriction**: Represents a range of time during which CallFire will send a call or text to recipients. Timeframe uses the local timezone of recipient's number",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**beginHour**: An hour of restriction start",
                  "**beginMinute**: The minutes to start a restriction",
                  "**enabled**: A restriction enabled",
                  "**endHour**: An hour of restriction end",
                  "**endMinute**: The minutes of restriction end"
                ]
              }
            ],
            "**maxActive**: A maximum number of texts that CallFire dials at once",
            "**media**: ~",
            "**message**: A text message",
            "**name**: A name of a broadcast",
            "**recipients**: Recipients of a text campaign, can be an existing contacts or a new one",
            "**resumeNextDay**: ~",
            "**schedules**: ~",
            "**status**: A status of a broadcast. SETUP - campaign isn't configured yet; START_PENDING - waiting for contact batch population; RUNNING - campaign is running; STOPPED - campaign is stopped; FINISHED - campaign is finished; ARCHIVED - campaign was archived"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
